data.description: Welcome to your lakeside oasis in Punta Gorda! This beautifully updated 3-bed, 2-bath home represents the pinnacle of contemporary living. It's now back on the market after undergoing numerous renovations that have significantly enhanced its value. The focal point of this home is its newly transformed kitchen, featuring quartz countertops, a new sink/faucet, and refreshed cabinetry. The custom coffee bar adds an element of sophistication, creating an ideal space to savor your morning coffee. The bathrooms showcase stylish updates including, a newly tiled shower, new vanity tops and mirrors. This home also boasts a new roof, A/C, water heater, interiors/exterior paint, luxury vinyl flooring, and new appliances, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. Outside you'll discover an expansive backyard with a oversized Florida room overlooking a serene lake - perfect for a future pool. Burnt Store Lakes offers an array of community amenities, including a fishing pier and park. Optional memberships for golf, fitness, tennis, and a marina are also available. Conveniently situated near shopping, dining, schools, and beaches, this home serves as your gateway to the Florida lifestyle dream.
